name: Grumpy bear plush
description:
Grumpy bear plush-Assorted colors


Bear can be a pretty grumpy fur ball. But deep down inside he is a sweet and cuddley bear, shhh don't tell! Perfect for scaring away under the bed monsters, or just being a fuzzy friend.
Bear is made from eco friendly felt. Inside he is stuffed with soft fill perfect for snuggling. Bear has sturdy black plastic eyes. 

Bear measures: 8.75 x 6.75 inches, or 22.2 x 17.1 cm

Choose from light brown, black, white, or gray colored bears!

name: Luchador Thumb Wrestlers
description:
Luchador thumb wrestlers are here, and they are ready to kick butt!

Each luchador is free hand-cut by myself and are made of felt. You get 2 luchadors in a blind assortment of colors. Each one just slips over your thumb ready for some thumb wrestling action! 
Lucadors come on a card that has blank name banners for you to fill in your favorite Lucha names!


Luchadors measure: 2.5 x 1.5 inches, or 6.4 x 3.8 cm

If you would like a custom combo of colors, please just drop us a line!

name: Yum buttons! Assorted styles
description:
Buttons are an assortment of  cute and yummy kawaii style foods! Buttons are han made from clay and are hand painted. I also give all yum buttons a clear coat of sealer to make them extra protected! Each yum button has a sturdy pin clasp on the back. Ready and yummy to wear on any outfit!

Button measures: 1.75 inches round, or 4.4cm

Choose from: Chocolate chip cookie, Sushi, Pickle, Cupcake, Sunday breakfast, or Chocolate cupcake!

name: Matryoshka doll zip pouch
description:
Pouch is made from red fabric with tiny white polks dots. Inside is lined in blue and cream vintage floral fabric. All edges of fabric are finished to prevent fraying. Pouch has a black sturdy zipper to keep all your goodies safe! Front is adorn with a matryoshka or Russian doll Japanese ribbon. Pouch is perfect for carrying all your purse odds-n-ends and goodies!

Pouch measures: 4 x 6 inches, or 10.2 x 15.2 cm

name: Vintage camera series- Falcon pouch
description:
Pouch is made from white cotton with custom image of a vintage falcon minicam junior. The back is black with white dots. Inside is lined in linen. All edges are finished to prevent fraying.
I have a love for the design, history and charm of vintage cameras. Each pouch from the series will feature a vintage camera from my own personal collection. 

Pouch measures: 6.25 x 4.5 inches, or 15.9 x 11.4 cm
